{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sigma Squad is a fast-paced, competitive multiplayer FPS that takes the classic genre experience to a new level of precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cWhat you see is what you get,\u201d some say. In Sigma Squad, we have that too, but with one difference\u2014it actually works here. With 256-tickrate servers, we guarantee smooth gameplay and precise shots that let you trust every move you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/256_tickrate__2_.gif?t=1733400661\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore five unique maps, each inspired by different cultures and iconic spots:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Freedom Land</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maiameee</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hong</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Japanese Sunset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;The day&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Created by a small, family-run indie studio with over 10 years of experience in technology development, <i>Sigma Squad</i> represents our passion for the genre and our desire to deliver an enhanced and precise experience for both casual and competitive players alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We greatly appreciate your support in adding Sigma Squad to your wishlist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/extras/Add_a_subheading.png?t=1733400661\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733400661","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249210/page.bg.jpg?t=1733400661","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store